VIPKILLA's FusionPBX:

Some improvements include:

    Inbound Numbers Manager
    Quick Add user option
    Global Permissions option (default is on)
    Email based login to eliminate the need for multiple domain logins (default is on)
    Set toll allow permissions for each domain as superadmin 

Currently in progress:

    Feature codes
    Caller Routes 
    LUA based dialplan and directory (to eliminate the need for static XML)

More to come including:

    Billing Engine
    FreeSWITCH node manager
    Simplified Menus